WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.110
Hey, good morning family. How are you all doing

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:05.550
today? I'm going to talk to you all

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:08.790
about the angels. If you watched

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.110
my last video, I was starting to talk

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:13.509
about that, but then the Lord took

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:16.070
that in a different direction, talking

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:17.990
about the blessing. So, I'm going to talk

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.150
to you all about the angelic visitations

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:25.870
that I've had.

00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:28.509
I've had several angelic

00:00:28.519 --> 00:00:31.669
visitations and the Lord has been amazing

00:00:31.679 --> 00:00:33.190
over the years; I've seen some really

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:35.510
cool stuff.

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:38.869
But this time, we were just

00:00:38.879 --> 00:00:41.110
praying. It was a normal night

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:43.750
in the same house;

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:45.950
everything was the same.

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:48.709
We were praying and we went to

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:51.950
bed, and all of a sudden my wife and I

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:55.430
were woken up out of our sleep

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:58.590
around 2:00 or 3:00 in the morning.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:03.069
The whole house shook. It sounded like

00:01:03.079 --> 00:01:05.109
the whole roof was going to

00:01:05.119 --> 00:01:08.789
come off of our house. My wife said,

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.630
'Oh, did you hear that?'and she woke me.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:13.310
I said, 'Yes, I heard it; it woke me up too.

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:14.990
I think somebody's trying to

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.710
break into our house. Let me

00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:20.510
go check.'I grabbed my pistol and I

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:22.069
went

00:01:22.069 --> 00:01:22.079
to

00:01:22.079 --> 00:01:23.710
check our home to make

00:01:23.720 --> 00:01:27.789
sure that nobody was

00:01:27.789 --> 00:01:27.799
in there.

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:31.069
All of a sudden, I looked out. I'm

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:33.590
standing by the door and

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:36.550
my eyes

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:42.469
are opened to the spirit realm. I see

00:01:42.479 --> 00:01:46.429
four

00:01:46.429 --> 00:01:46.439
demons—four

00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:50.109
demonic spirits that were shaped with

00:01:50.119 --> 00:01:51.950
scales all over

00:01:51.960 --> 00:01:55.389
them. They had

00:01:55.389 --> 00:01:55.399
nasty-looking

00:01:55.399 --> 00:01:58.630
hair growing out of them and

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:02.630
warts on them. Their eyes were shaped

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:05.069
slanted, like red

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:08.350
eyes. One was with a pig-looking nose

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:11.390
with tusks coming up. Then the other one

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:14.630
was completely black;

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.830
there was no shape to it. It looked kind

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:19.949
of like

00:02:19.959 --> 00:02:22.390
a ghost, but it was just a

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:25.270
black, misty-looking thing. The

00:02:25.270 --> 00:02:25.280
others were

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:26.670
different

00:02:26.670 --> 00:02:26.680
shapes.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:27.710
I'm not going to

00:02:27.720 --> 00:02:30.030
give any more glory to it, but every

00:02:30.040 --> 00:02:31.390
single one of them was there, and

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:34.110
they were trying to get into the

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:36.790
house. They shook the

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:40.350
roof of the house in the natural

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:42.110
and, like I said, it startled both of us

00:02:42.120 --> 00:02:45.149
and woke us up, but they couldn't get

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:48.070
in. At the time,

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:51.750
I could see them grunting and hissing and

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:55.110
doing all kinds of stuff, carrying on by

00:02:55.110 --> 00:02:55.120
us

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.509
on the street, but I didn't

00:02:57.519 --> 00:02:59.070
understand why they couldn't come past. All

00:02:59.070 --> 00:02:59.080
of a

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:01.910
sudden, I

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:04.550
saw massive

00:03:04.550 --> 00:03:04.560
angels—humongous

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:06.110
angels—chained

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:09.190
together. Their

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:11.949
arms were chained together,

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:13.789
like when you

00:03:13.799 --> 00:03:15.830
cross your arms with each other.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.470
They were standing strong, and those

00:03:45.470 --> 00:03:45.480
demonic spirits

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:47.750
were hitting against those

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:50.710
angelic beings,

00:03:50.710 --> 00:03:50.720
but

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:53.429
they couldn't get past them.

00:03:53.439 --> 00:03:56.069
Every night before we go to bed, we put

00:03:56.069 --> 00:03:56.079
chain-linked

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:58.869
angels all around our house

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:00.990
and we commission them. We thank you, Lord,

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.350
that the angels are surrounding our

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.910
house, that no devil in hell can come

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.270
across the bloodline and

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:10.789
cannot come across the angels. The angels

00:04:10.799 --> 00:04:12.910
are protecting us as we

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:17.390
sleep. It was just like we prayed.

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:19.509
This is part of what I'm trying

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:21.390
to tell you all about.

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:25.469
It took me back so much

00:04:25.479 --> 00:04:29.310
that I yelled when I saw this,

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:34.710
'Praise God! Wow! Praise the

00:04:34.710 --> 00:04:34.720
Lord!'because

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:38.230
I saw the angels protecting us.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:41.189
Whenever they heard me praising the

00:04:41.199 --> 00:04:43.110
Lord, they

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:46.230
all looked over, turned their

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:49.469
bodies, started looking at me, and

00:04:49.479 --> 00:04:53.670
they said, 'Praise the Lord!'and they started

00:04:53.670 --> 00:04:53.680
worshipping

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:56.629
the Lord with me. I turned

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:59.150
around and I said,

00:04:59.150 --> 00:04:59.160
'Whoa!'because

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:02.670
it was so loud. Their voices

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:07.029
were so loud they sounded like sirens,

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:10.510
like trumpets, like a blast.

00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:13.590
They said it

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:20.990
together: 'Praise

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.670
the Lord!'And when they did, it echoed

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:25.430
throughout all the area; you could hear

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:26.990
it in the spirit realm. It was

00:05:26.990 --> 00:05:27.000
so loud you'd

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.590
have to hold

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:30.270
your ears.

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:32.510
They started

00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:34.830
praising the Lord with me. Every

00:05:34.840 --> 00:05:37.230
single time they worshipped the Lord,

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:40.270
they

00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:43.150
turned back to see what I was doing.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:46.150
As

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:48.029
I praised the Lord, they started praising

00:05:48.039 --> 00:05:50.150
the Lord. It became a chain, and we

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:52.430
just started praising the Lord. At that

00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:56.710
time, I saw the glory coming from the

00:05:56.720 --> 00:05:59.950
heavens through the dimensions,

00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:02.510
through the portal. I could see

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:07.510
shafts of light coming through

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:10.629
that portal and it was making those

00:06:10.639 --> 00:06:14.950
angels glow. They started glowing with a

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:18.230
heavenly glory glow, even brighter as

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:21.430
they praised the Lord. Those shafts of

00:06:21.440 --> 00:06:23.950
light were coming out of the

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:26.390
heavens and

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:34.550
it was giving them 'super

00:06:34.550 --> 00:06:34.560
juice.'They

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:36.390
were praising the Lord

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:39.189
with me and they were getting more

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:42.270
shiny. I had completely forgotten about

00:06:42.280 --> 00:06:44.670
the demonic spirits that were there

00:06:44.670 --> 00:06:44.680
because

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:46.469
I was caught up in the glory of worshipping

00:06:46.469 --> 00:06:46.479
with

00:06:46.479 --> 00:06:49.309
the angels at the same time.

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:51.870
Every single time I said, 'Thank you,

00:06:51.870 --> 00:06:51.880
Jesus,'they

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:54.430
would say, 'Thank you,

00:06:55.950 --> 00:06:55.960
Jesus.'This

00:06:57.800 --> 00:07:00.029
went on for quite some time

00:07:01.879 --> 00:07:04.390
because I was taken back by what I was

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.629
seeing in the spirit realm;

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:09.469
it really was amazing.

00:07:09.479 --> 00:07:11.469
After all this happened, I saw the glory

00:07:11.479 --> 00:07:14.110
come down. It was

00:07:14.110 --> 00:07:14.120
around 4:00

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:15.749
or 5:00 in the morning by

00:07:15.749 --> 00:07:15.759
then,

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:17.350
and I had to go to

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.629
work by 7:00, so I went and

00:07:19.639 --> 00:07:21.830
laid down a little bit and dozed off.

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.670
But it was really hard

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.869
to get any more

00:07:24.879 --> 00:07:25.670
rest.

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:28.869
I got to work the next day at the

00:07:28.879 --> 00:07:30.110
church

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:33.710
and we had an all-staff meeting.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:36.510
The pastor of the church, Pastor Mark, saw

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:37.830
me because I was sitting in the front.

00:07:37.840 --> 00:07:39.909
I told him, 'I want to tell you

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.909
what happened last night.'He

00:07:41.909 --> 00:07:41.919
said,

00:07:41.919 --> 00:07:44.430
'Brandon, I don't doubt it at all.

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:46.510
As you were talking, you

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:46.520
were

00:07:46.520 --> 00:07:48.950
shining. I can see the glory shining

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:51.149
on you. There is actually a presence of

00:07:51.159 --> 00:07:53.029
the Lord that's shining on you.'It was

00:07:53.039 --> 00:07:55.670
still on me from the night

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:58.469
before, from having the visitation

00:07:58.479 --> 00:08:01.950
from the angels, and it was actually

00:08:01.960 --> 00:08:04.350
making me shine a little bit,

00:08:04.350 --> 00:08:04.360
from

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:06.430
what Pastor Mark said.

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:12.350
It's just amazing.

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:14.830
I

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:18.070
live by faith; I live this way. I

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.950
expect angelic visitations and

00:08:20.960 --> 00:08:23.830
manifestations of the glory in my house.

00:08:23.840 --> 00:08:27.029
I expect God to do the impossible and I

00:08:27.039 --> 00:08:29.550
receive it.

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:31.189
Let me tell you another one.

00:08:31.189 --> 00:08:31.199
There've

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:32.709
been times

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:34.469
whenever I'm going through a shady part

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:36.389
of town and I'm nervous. There was

00:08:36.399 --> 00:08:38.750
this one time I was going to

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:40.909
the gas station and it was pretty late

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:42.670
at night.

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.269
During the winter it seems late

00:08:47.279 --> 00:08:50.150
because the sun goes down so early.

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:52.230
I went to the gas station to put gas

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:54.350
in the car and I was nervous to get out

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:56.750
because of where I was.

00:08:59.480 --> 00:09:02.350
All of a sudden,

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:04.870
because God

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.670
loves you all—God is a God

00:09:06.680 --> 00:09:10.190
of love and he's

00:09:10.190 --> 00:09:10.200
compassionate—just

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:13.389
for my comfort, he opened my

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:15.630
eyes. He said, 'Look over, son.'I looked

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:18.910
over to my left

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:18.920
and

00:09:18.920 --> 00:09:20.350
there was a

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:23.949
massive, massive angel standing there

00:09:23.959 --> 00:09:27.870
watching over me as I was pumping gas

00:09:27.880 --> 00:09:31.470
in my car. The angel was at attention. He

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:35.190
had muscles upon muscles; he made Arnold

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:37.870
Schwarzenegger look like a little

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:41.069
baby wimpy guy,

00:09:41.079 --> 00:09:43.430
or even some big bodybuilder, a Mr.

00:09:43.430 --> 00:09:43.440
Olympia

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:45.230
who

00:09:45.230 --> 00:09:45.240
is

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:47.269
ripped.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:52.790
This angel had muscle upon

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:55.470
muscle and he was standing there decked

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.790
out with this garment, which looked

00:09:57.800 --> 00:09:59.910
like some kind of armor, and he was

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:03.750
looking out at attention, watching over

00:10:03.760 --> 00:10:07.750
me. When I saw that, it

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:10.470
took my breath

00:10:12.509 --> 00:10:12.519
away.

00:10:16.399 --> 00:10:19.829
It blessed me. As he was

00:10:19.839 --> 00:10:22.870
watching out for me, it just shows that we

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:25.670
have angels that keep charge over us and

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:28.350
they bear us up in their hands, lest we

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:31.630
dash our foot against a stone. He

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:33.670
promised us in Psalm 91

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:36.030
that he would

00:10:36.040 --> 00:10:39.310
take care of us. Do you believe

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:42.190
that Jesus is still the same

00:10:42.200 --> 00:10:44.470
yesterday, today, and forever? What he

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:46.470
would do for the people in the Bible,

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:49.710
he'll do for you. Let

00:10:49.720 --> 00:10:51.590
me tell you another

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:54.710
one. I was working at the

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:57.110
church and I've told you all about

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.389
the healings when I led prayer

00:10:59.399 --> 00:11:01.430
and the angels bringing in hearts for

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.910
people.

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:06.509
It was another heart

00:11:06.519 --> 00:11:08.990
testimony. I was vacuuming

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:11.629
the floor and I was seeing into

00:11:11.629 --> 00:11:11.639
the

00:11:11.639 --> 00:11:13.470
realm of the spirits.

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:16.949
This time, the angel

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:20.470
touched me, and I literally thought I was

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.829
going to come up out of my skin

00:11:22.829 --> 00:11:22.839
because

00:11:22.839 --> 00:11:25.990
I felt it on my shoulder.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:29.470
I was the only one in the room

00:11:29.470 --> 00:11:29.480
vacuuming

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:32.590
the church and I went,

00:11:32.590 --> 00:11:32.600
'Whoa!'You

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:35.030
get a little startled when

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:35.040
an

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:37.710
angel touches you like that.

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:39.629
I turned around and I

00:11:39.629 --> 00:11:39.639
was

00:11:39.639 --> 00:11:41.150
seeing in the realm of the spirit—it

00:11:41.150 --> 00:11:41.160
wasn't a

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:43.550
physical manifestation, but I

00:11:43.550 --> 00:11:43.560
saw him

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:45.829
in the realm

00:11:45.839 --> 00:11:47.230
of the spirit—but he touched me in the

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:50.509
natural. He said, 'I've come to give

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:52.389
Jim a

00:11:52.399 --> 00:11:54.829
heart. You need to go and tell

00:11:54.839 --> 00:11:56.670
Jim that I've brought him a heart.'Jim

00:11:56.670 --> 00:11:56.680
was

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.269
believing and praying for a

00:11:59.279 --> 00:12:00.710
miracle because

00:12:00.710 --> 00:12:00.720
he

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:02.430
had a bad heart. He was one of

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:05.310
the other janitors on staff and his

00:12:05.320 --> 00:12:08.629
blood pressure would drop really bad;

00:12:08.639 --> 00:12:10.069
he would have to go to the ER all

00:12:10.079 --> 00:12:12.470
the time. It was very serious.

00:12:14.959 --> 00:12:17.350
The angel brought this heart

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:19.430
and I could see it in the spirit realm as clearly

00:12:19.430 --> 00:12:19.440
as I see

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.189
my son right now.

00:12:21.199 --> 00:12:23.509
The angel had

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:26.389
a heart in

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:31.389
both hands.

00:12:31.399 --> 00:12:32.949
He brought it to

00:12:32.959 --> 00:12:35.949
me and he said, 'Go and tell Jim that I

00:12:35.959 --> 00:12:39.629
brought the heart for him.'I said, 'Wow,

00:12:39.639 --> 00:12:41.910
what an honor.'So

00:12:41.910 --> 00:12:41.920
I walked

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:44.310
all the way down

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:46.910
the hall. Jim was in room number two

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:51.910
or

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:53.990
three.

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:01.430
I walked in

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:03.069
there and the angel went in there. I

00:13:03.079 --> 00:13:05.470
told Jim, 'Jim,

00:13:05.480 --> 00:13:08.110
there's an angel of the Lord here and he

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:10.949
has brought you a heart. Do you

00:13:10.959 --> 00:13:12.509
want to receive it? I'm going to pray for

00:13:12.519 --> 00:13:13.790
you and you're going to receive this

00:13:13.790 --> 00:13:13.800
heart.'He

00:13:13.800 --> 00:13:17.310
said, 'Man, you aren't seeing

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:20.350
nothing, dude. You're crazy,

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:22.509
get out of here.'He was totally pooh-poohing me, like

00:13:22.509 --> 00:13:22.519
I

00:13:22.519 --> 00:13:24.949
was

00:13:24.959 --> 00:13:27.710
a weirdo. I

00:13:27.710 --> 00:13:27.720
said,

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:29.790
'No, really, I

00:13:29.800 --> 00:13:32.590
see an angelic being. He

00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:33.910
wants to bring you

00:13:33.910 --> 00:13:33.920
a

00:13:33.920 --> 00:13:35.629
heart. Do you want the heart?'He goes,

00:13:35.639 --> 00:13:37.350
'Dude, get out of here, stop bothering me.

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:38.949
That's

00:13:38.949 --> 00:13:38.959
weird.'I

00:13:38.959 --> 00:13:41.430
was

00:13:41.430 --> 00:13:41.440
a

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:44.710
little

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:47.230
offended.

00:13:47.230 --> 00:13:47.240
I

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:49.269
told

00:13:49.269 --> 00:13:49.279
the

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:50.910
angel,

00:13:50.920 --> 00:13:52.470
'He

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:54.710
doesn't

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:56.670
want the heart. You hear

00:13:56.680 --> 00:13:58.829
what he just said?

00:13:58.839 --> 00:14:00.590
I'm out of here.'I walked away.

00:14:00.600 --> 00:14:03.749
I go

00:14:03.759 --> 00:14:06.189
back and

00:14:06.199 --> 00:14:08.590
I'm vacuuming the floors.

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:11.069
The angel of the Lord taps me on the

00:14:11.079 --> 00:14:14.430
shoulder again. He said, 'Go one more time

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:17.710
and ask Jim if he wants this

00:14:17.710 --> 00:14:17.720
heart.'I

00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:20.030
said, 'You heard what he said. He

00:14:20.030 --> 00:14:20.040
doesn't

00:14:20.040 --> 00:14:21.870
believe me and he made fun

00:14:21.880 --> 00:14:23.749
of

00:14:23.749 --> 00:14:23.759
me.'He

00:14:23.759 --> 00:14:26.629
said, 'Just go ask him one more

00:14:26.629 --> 00:14:26.639
time.'So

00:14:26.639 --> 00:14:30.350
I went down and I said,

00:14:30.360 --> 00:14:33.350
'Jim, I'm coming because the angel

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:36.189
asked me to ask you one more time: do you

00:14:36.199 --> 00:14:40.749
want this heart?'He said, 'You really do

00:14:40.759 --> 00:14:43.590
see something, don't you,

00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:46.430
Brandon?'I

00:14:46.440 --> 00:14:48.749
said, 'Yeah, I'm

00:14:48.759 --> 00:14:50.150
telling you, he's standing right there.'I

00:14:50.150 --> 00:14:50.160
described

00:14:50.160 --> 00:14:52.470
what he looked like. He

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:55.910
goes, 'Well, yeah, I need

00:14:55.910 --> 00:14:55.920
healing.'I

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.990
went over and I said, 'In the name

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:01.110
of Jesus, I command you to be healed

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:03.829
of this heart condition.'I watched

00:15:03.839 --> 00:15:07.949
that angel drop that heart

00:15:07.959 --> 00:15:10.069
inside of Jim's

00:15:10.079 --> 00:15:12.550
chest. I said, 'I believe you

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:13.910
received it, brother.'The angel

00:15:13.920 --> 00:15:18.470
disappeared

00:15:18.480 --> 00:15:21.350
instantaneously. Within 24

00:15:21.360 --> 00:15:22.550
hours,

00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:25.910
he

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.870
started

00:15:27.880 --> 00:15:29.670
getting better. Now, I don't

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:32.509
know where Jim is at now,

00:15:33.920 --> 00:15:36.269
but I'm telling you, at that

00:15:36.279 --> 00:15:38.990
moment, I believe Jim got a new heart and

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:42.910
his flesh started getting better.

00:15:42.910 --> 00:15:42.920
Later,

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:45.670
Jim got caught up in drugs and

00:15:45.680 --> 00:15:48.269
alcohol and he

00:15:48.279 --> 00:15:51.069
backslid really hard, but

00:15:53.959 --> 00:15:56.430
at that moment, I believe

00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:59.910
with all my heart Jesus Christ gave Jim

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.990
a heart and the angel

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.030
brought it. I wanted to encourage you

00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:06.470
all about that one.

00:16:09.160 --> 00:16:12.030
I have so many

00:16:12.040 --> 00:16:14.629
visitations and

00:16:14.639 --> 00:16:16.790
manifestations of the

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:19.749
glory. I've told you all about

00:16:19.759 --> 00:16:22.230
my truck supernaturally

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:24.150
getting pushed down the highway for two and

00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:24.160
a half

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:26.910
miles.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:36.870
We were pushed by

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:38.590
an angel.

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:41.309
We ran out of gas; the

00:16:41.319 --> 00:16:43.829
gas gauge was out

00:16:43.829 --> 00:16:43.839
and

00:16:43.839 --> 00:16:45.629
I had forgotten

00:16:45.629 --> 00:16:45.639
to

00:16:45.639 --> 00:16:48.829
put gas in. We drove a long way to work.

00:16:48.839 --> 00:16:51.189
My wife

00:16:51.199 --> 00:16:52.629
was pregnant with my

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:55.430
daughter at the time, and my other two children

00:16:55.430 --> 00:16:55.440
were

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:58.069
in the back. It

00:16:58.069 --> 00:16:58.079
was a

00:16:58.079 --> 00:17:01.509
hot

00:17:01.519 --> 00:17:04.230
summer day in the middle of July.

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:09.270
My truck turns off in the middle

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:12.309
of the highway. I go over to the side,

00:17:12.319 --> 00:17:14.630
put my hazard lights on, and told

00:17:14.640 --> 00:17:17.350
my wife,

00:17:17.360 --> 00:17:18.870
'Baby, I'm going to have to

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:20.789
walk to the gas station.'She's big

00:17:20.799 --> 00:17:24.110
and pregnant and I'm thinking this is

00:17:24.120 --> 00:17:28.669
going to be really bad.

00:17:28.669 --> 00:17:28.679
We

00:17:28.679 --> 00:17:30.430
start praying in the spirit.

00:17:32.039 --> 00:17:35.549
Lo and behold, we have this

00:17:35.559 --> 00:17:39.270
massive boom. I thought somebody had

00:17:39.270 --> 00:17:39.280
rear-ended

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:42.350
us.

00:17:42.360 --> 00:17:45.390
Our whole truck jerked and all of a

00:17:45.400 --> 00:17:47.990
sudden we started going faster and

00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:50.870
faster down the

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:53.190
highway. I put my blinker on and I'm

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:55.190
riding on the shoulder,

00:17:55.190 --> 00:17:55.200
then

00:17:55.200 --> 00:17:57.830
I merge onto the highway

00:17:57.840 --> 00:17:59.590
with the engine off.

00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:01.390
Whether you want to believe this or not,

00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:02.350
it's the

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:05.630
truth. We're going 70

00:18:05.630 --> 00:18:05.640
miles

00:18:05.640 --> 00:18:10.070
an hour with the engine off, passing

00:18:10.080 --> 00:18:13.950
people in the left-hand lane.

00:18:13.950 --> 00:18:13.960
That

00:18:13.960 --> 00:18:16.190
angel

00:18:16.190 --> 00:18:16.200
pushed

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:19.990
us all the way

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:24.029
down. We took the exit and

00:18:24.029 --> 00:18:24.039
stopped

00:18:24.039 --> 00:18:26.990
at the stoplight; the angel

00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:27.000
pushed

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:29.350
us through the stoplight,

00:18:29.350 --> 00:18:29.360
then

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:31.430
turned

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:33.789
right

00:18:33.789 --> 00:18:33.799
and

00:18:33.799 --> 00:18:36.470
pushed

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:39.149
us

00:18:39.159 --> 00:18:41.789
right in front of the pump. We all

00:18:41.799 --> 00:18:43.789
started screaming and praising the Lord

00:18:43.799 --> 00:18:45.789
because it was so supernatural.

00:18:45.799 --> 00:18:47.990
Other

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:49.630
people at the pumps were looking

00:18:49.640 --> 00:18:51.789
at us, wondering what was going on.

00:18:51.799 --> 00:18:54.029
It

00:18:54.039 --> 00:18:55.350
was

00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:57.549
one of those moments

00:18:57.549 --> 00:18:57.559
when

00:18:57.559 --> 00:18:59.669
you're shaking because of

00:18:59.679 --> 00:19:02.070
what's happening in the natural.

00:19:02.080 --> 00:19:04.149
God

00:19:04.149 --> 00:19:04.159
came

00:19:04.159 --> 00:19:06.870
through for us again.

00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:10.510
I've told this story

00:19:10.520 --> 00:19:12.470
before, but it's worth telling again.

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:19.310
I've

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:26.549
told you about the angel coming

00:19:26.559 --> 00:19:29.110
in when we were believing

00:19:29.120 --> 00:19:31.230
for the puppies to be raised from the dead.

00:19:33.950 --> 00:19:33.960
A

00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:38.510
little baby girl angel came

00:19:38.520 --> 00:19:41.470
in and laid

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:43.830
hands on Alice, and all those puppies

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:45.630
came out. Then I told you all about

00:19:53.919 --> 00:19:57.590
the hospital where my wife had no pain. An

00:19:57.590 --> 00:19:57.600
angel

00:19:57.600 --> 00:20:01.110
came in and laid

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:02.990
hands on my wife during our first

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:04.710
pregnancy. We were believing for a

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:08.029
supernatural childbirth

00:20:08.029 --> 00:20:08.039
with

00:20:08.039 --> 00:20:10.669
no pain.

00:20:10.679 --> 00:20:13.870
My wife was in labor

00:20:13.880 --> 00:20:16.669
with our daughter, Megan.

00:20:16.679 --> 00:20:20.029
The angel came in and laid

00:20:20.039 --> 00:20:23.710
his hands on her stomach, and

00:20:23.720 --> 00:20:26.549
until my wife was almost

00:20:26.559 --> 00:20:29.149
completely through delivery, she felt

00:20:29.159 --> 00:20:31.230
nothing. She felt

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:33.470
contractions,

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:36.070
but she had no

00:20:36.080 --> 00:20:39.029
pain at all. Even the doctor

00:20:39.039 --> 00:20:41.350
and the people coming

00:20:41.350 --> 00:20:41.360
in—family

00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:43.350
trying to

00:20:44.990 --> 00:20:45.000
visit—some

00:20:46.600 --> 00:20:48.110
would

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:52.950
say,

00:20:53.760 --> 00:20:56.669
'That's impossible.'All

00:20:56.669 --> 00:20:56.679
of a

00:20:56.679 --> 00:20:58.870
sudden,

00:20:58.880 --> 00:21:00.350
that angel took his hand away because there was so

00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:01.990
much doubt and unbelief in the room.

00:21:05.400 --> 00:21:09.029
You get shaken by people speaking

00:21:09.039 --> 00:21:11.830
negative things around you about what God's

00:21:11.840 --> 00:21:14.350
doing. Even the doctor was saying it

00:21:14.350 --> 00:21:14.360
was

00:21:14.360 --> 00:21:16.430
impossible. The nurses

00:21:16.440 --> 00:21:18.149
all look at you like you're wild.

00:21:18.159 --> 00:21:20.510
They don't understand how my

00:21:20.520 --> 00:21:23.310
wife was not having any pain during

00:21:23.320 --> 00:21:25.990
childbirth.

00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:28.789
But this

00:21:28.789 --> 00:21:28.799
is

00:21:28.799 --> 00:21:31.470
very important:

00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:34.269
do not let

00:21:34.279 --> 00:21:37.269
negativity into your hospital room

00:21:37.279 --> 00:21:40.350
when you are believing for a miracle,

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:43.950
because it's a robber of your faith.

00:21:46.559 --> 00:21:48.029
Just like faith comes by hearing

00:21:48.039 --> 00:21:49.470
the word of God, doubt

00:21:49.480 --> 00:21:51.510
comes by hearing fear.

00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:54.029
When Jesus

00:21:54.039 --> 00:21:55.830
was raising the little girl from the

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:59.110
dead, he made all the other people

00:21:59.120 --> 00:22:03.190
leave the room because they didn't have faith. He

00:22:03.190 --> 00:22:03.200
got them

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:06.149
out of the

00:22:06.159 --> 00:22:09.350
house.

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:11.909
Doubt and unbelief rob

00:22:11.909 --> 00:22:11.919
you

00:22:11.919 --> 00:22:14.630
of what you're believing for.

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:16.909
Sometimes you've got to get people

00:22:16.919 --> 00:22:19.110
out of

00:22:20.679 --> 00:22:22.909
your

00:22:22.919 --> 00:22:25.190
room because they speak doubt.

00:22:25.200 --> 00:22:29.029
If Jesus

00:22:29.039 --> 00:22:32.510
were

00:22:32.520 --> 00:22:35.350
on the earth today doing miracles, he would tell you

00:22:35.350 --> 00:22:35.360
to leave the room

00:22:35.360 --> 00:22:37.710
if

00:22:37.720 --> 00:22:40.230
you

00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:42.830
didn't

00:22:42.840 --> 00:22:44.990
have faith.

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:49.590
You've got to be

00:22:49.590 --> 00:22:49.600
like

00:22:49.600 --> 00:22:52.230
a bulldog on a bone; you've got to

00:22:52.240 --> 00:22:54.750
believe God for your miracle and not let

00:22:54.760 --> 00:22:56.590
the devil come in through doubt and

00:22:56.600 --> 00:22:59.390
unbelief to rob you of your

00:22:59.400 --> 00:23:01.590
victories.

00:23:09.520 --> 00:23:12.190
I'm telling you this because the Lord

00:23:12.200 --> 00:23:16.029
told me it's time for his body to

00:23:16.039 --> 00:23:19.669
start commissioning their angels, saying,

00:23:19.679 --> 00:23:22.750
'Father, I thank you that the angels are

00:23:22.760 --> 00:23:25.390
watching over me today; they will bear me

00:23:25.400 --> 00:23:27.310
up in their hands, lest I dash my foot

00:23:27.320 --> 00:23:29.669
against a stone,'based on Psalm 91. I

00:23:29.679 --> 00:23:31.750
thank you that angels are watching me

00:23:31.760 --> 00:23:35.710
from the north, the south, the east, and the

00:23:35.720 --> 00:23:38.950
west. I call in for

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.510
prosperity. I thank you that the

00:23:40.520 --> 00:23:42.110
angels are

00:23:42.120 --> 00:23:43.710
bringing

00:23:43.720 --> 00:23:46.590
finances to me and giving me

00:23:46.600 --> 00:23:50.029
favor.

00:23:52.919 --> 00:23:55.390
Keep your angels busy. People say

00:23:55.400 --> 00:23:56.310
you don't have authority over your

00:23:56.320 --> 00:23:59.590
angels. The same Jesus Christ

00:23:59.590 --> 00:23:59.600
who

00:23:59.600 --> 00:24:02.190
had

00:24:02.200 --> 00:24:04.590
authority over the angels

00:24:04.600 --> 00:24:06.549
dwells on

00:24:06.559 --> 00:24:10.390
the inside of you.

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:19.909
If he is

00:24:19.919 --> 00:24:21.990
dwelling in you and you're seated with

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:24.669
him in the heavenlies,

00:24:24.679 --> 00:24:27.430
you

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:30.389
have it inside of you to do what he

00:24:30.399 --> 00:24:33.990
did. The Bible says, 'Be ye imitators of

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:36.110
God as dear children imitate their

00:24:36.110 --> 00:24:36.120
father.'If

00:24:39.110 --> 00:24:39.120
we

00:24:39.120 --> 00:24:42.350
are

00:24:42.360 --> 00:24:45.789
as

00:24:45.789 --> 00:24:45.799
he

00:24:50.190 --> 00:24:50.200
is

00:24:50.200 --> 00:24:54.710
and

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:57.430
we're supposed to

00:24:57.440 --> 00:24:59.830
imitate

00:24:59.840 --> 00:25:04.470
him,

00:25:19.559 --> 00:25:22.470
we have power to

00:25:22.480 --> 00:25:24.950
commission our

00:25:24.960 --> 00:25:28.909
angels just as he does.

00:25:28.919 --> 00:25:32.590
We

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:35.149
are seated with him in the heavenlies,

00:25:35.159 --> 00:25:37.070
just like Ephesians talks about. You all

00:25:37.080 --> 00:25:39.430
need to read

00:25:39.440 --> 00:25:42.070
who you are in Christ.

00:25:43.559 --> 00:25:46.230
I'm telling

00:25:46.230 --> 00:25:46.240
you:

00:25:46.240 --> 00:25:48.190
do that with your

00:25:48.200 --> 00:25:51.470
angels. It works.

00:25:53.960 --> 00:25:56.510
I can

00:25:56.520 --> 00:25:58.870
have what the word says I can have,

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:01.830
and you can too. He's

00:26:01.840 --> 00:26:04.389
no respecter of persons. I made that

00:26:04.399 --> 00:26:06.510
as simple as I could because

00:26:06.520 --> 00:26:08.230
some people are very religious and

00:26:08.240 --> 00:26:09.830
thick when it comes to

00:26:09.830 --> 00:26:09.840
the

00:26:09.840 --> 00:26:11.990
supernatural.

00:26:14.679 --> 00:26:16.190
Don't let the

00:26:16.200 --> 00:26:17.389
comment section tell you

00:26:17.389 --> 00:26:17.399
that you

00:26:17.399 --> 00:26:18.430
have no power

00:26:18.430 --> 00:26:18.440
or

00:26:18.440 --> 00:26:20.110
authority over angels.

00:26:20.120 --> 00:26:22.909
I'm an imitator of God. I'm a

00:26:22.909 --> 00:26:22.919
joint-heir

00:26:22.919 --> 00:26:25.630
of Jesus Christ. I can do what Jesus says

00:26:25.640 --> 00:26:27.750
I can do.

00:26:31.960 --> 00:26:34.750
He's no respecter of persons. So

00:26:34.760 --> 00:26:37.110
be

00:26:37.120 --> 00:26:39.549
active with your angels. They

00:26:39.549 --> 00:26:39.559
are

00:26:39.559 --> 00:26:42.110
ministering spirits sent

00:26:42.120 --> 00:26:45.110
to help you.

00:26:50.840 --> 00:26:53.029
Father, I thank you

00:26:53.039 --> 00:26:55.269
right now in the name of Jesus

00:26:55.279 --> 00:26:56.549
for every person

00:26:56.559 --> 00:26:58.830
here. We call them healed and

00:26:58.840 --> 00:27:01.230
whole. We thank you for your

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:03.990
angelic beings. Your angels are sent

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:05.630
forth to minister to the heirs of

00:27:05.640 --> 00:27:07.950
salvation. I thank you, Father, that

